{"tid":2241221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"激光耀獅山  籲關注12港青","createTime":"2020-10-13T07:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T07:32:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4cb0b3524f6083fd96ad84dd6beb2d255f6cb36f","tid":2241221,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:15:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201013/YIIOXA4XEFE7PC5T7P7GZIGSGE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201013%2FYIIOXA4XEFE7PC5T7P7GZIGSGE%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbQoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=8d7952e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201013%2FYIIOXA4XEFE7PC5T7P7GZIGSGE%2F&h=c6802343\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201013/YIIOXA4XEFE7PC5T7P7GZIGSGE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n激光耀獅山  籲關注12港青<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rmtm57J5P-CtQsEE4bHD9sHzLQ0=/2656x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B53DI5MOEJDHTCE4FGMV56NDTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Frmtm57J5P-CtQsEE4bHD9sHzLQ0%3D%2F2656x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FB53DI5MOEJDHTCE4FGMV56NDTM.jpg&h=606dce62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■香港民主女神團隊昨晚登上獅子山，並於山頂射出雷射燈光，冀各界關注被扣內地港青。路透社<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12名港青被扣於內地至今已逾個半月，各人現時仍被扣押在深圳鹽田看守所，特首林鄭月娥昨被問到會否探望12人時，卻指傳媒「每個禮拜都問呢啲問題」，表示「唔想再評論」。另外，「香港民主女神團隊」昨晚登上獅子山，於山頂射出12道雷射燈光，關注12名港青，他們要求中國政府立即移送12人回港，並呼籲國際社會持續關注事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭拒談 指記者「成日問」<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥昨日被問到，會否藉周三前往深圳出席深圳特區成立40周年慶祝大會的機會，向深圳當局轉達家屬欲探望被捕者的訴求，林鄭繼續表示不作評論，又指記者每星期都係「問呢個問題」。民主派斥林鄭無任何誠意為12名港人提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。。。，林鄭月娥只說：「每個禮拜喺（政府總部）呢度（記者）都係問呢啲問題。」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭又重彈舊調，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民主派會議召集人胡志偉批評，林鄭月娥的說法反映港府沒有任何誠意為12名港青提供協助，亦沒有將12名港青放在眼內：「特區政府根本完全無將香港人嘅利益放喺佢哋施政裏面，佢只係會以滿意中央政府要求，作為考慮所有問題嘅基礎，忘記咗佢應該要服務嘅係香港人。」"},{"pid":"a7489882e865a387454ab25fb10d7362f4271557","tid":2241221,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d513bf378fa4899c9fa654d7e53eba640fbc41","tid":2241221,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}